    "These tasks can be query-based or non-query-based.",
    "In this paper, as RAG retrieves information relevant to queries, we focus exclusively on query-based methods.• Recomp: Recomp [23] has extractive and abstractive compressors.",
    "The extractive compressor selects useful sentences, while the abstractive compressor synthesizes information from multiple documents.",
    "• LongLLMLingua: LongLLMLingua [49] improves LLMLingua by focusing on key information related to the query.",
    "• Selective Context Selective Context enhances LLM efficiency by identifying and removing redundant information in the input context."
